ltb / listtoolbar             Lists toolbar buttons used in 'internal' windows
 
   Format:
      ;ltb                    Lists toolbar buttons

   Notes:
      Toolbar buttons are used in many 'internal' windows, especially 'main'
         windows. When used, the same set of buttons are used each time.
      Use this command to show the toolbar buttons used, or use the
         ';edittoolbar' command to view settings for a particular button.
      Toolbar buttons can be added, deleted and modified in the client's
         preference window (use the ';editclient' command).
  
   User commands:
      ltb / listtool / listtoolbar
